Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,三連跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  可恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不愛我的那一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請同我一起赴死吧
