Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,9070 克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs65}出現高分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,完成四連跳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  太刀花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,超越天王杯那時的小新了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,從軟弱變成堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他繼續進行Prism Show好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這比我指導練習更適合他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吾為國立屋第七代傳人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太刀花雪之丞
